  <p class="dsv-note">A community resource from OIATC, the Ontario Indigenous AI and Technology Council, put together by Russell Jones, a Sagamok member. It explains how this technology works and what it means for community data. It is general information, not legal advice; for decisions that rely on the legal points, confirm with a privacy lawyer. Independent of Sagamok Chief and Council, and of Webflow, Memberstack, and the other companies named. Corrections welcome.</p>

</div>
